quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,97,"Say, "
  2,98,"Whoever is an enemy to Allāh and His angels and His messengers and Gabriel and Michael - then indeed, Allāh is an enemy to the disbelievers."
  2,99,"And We have certainly revealed to you verses [which are] clear proofs, and no one would deny them except the defiantly disobedient."
  3,37,"So her Lord accepted her with good acceptance and caused her to grow in a good manner and put her in the care of Zechariah. Every time Zechariah entered upon her in the prayer chamber, he found with her provision. He said, "
  3,38,"At that, Zechariah called upon his Lord, saying, "
  3,39,"So the angels called him while he was standing in prayer in the chamber, ",1:[Referring to the prophet Jesus (upon whom be peace) , who was conceived merely by a command from Allāh - the word "Be."]
